text: Lesley Kerkhove and Lidziya Marozava were the defending champions, but Marozava chose not to participate. Kerkhove partnered alongside Anna Blinkova and successfully defended her title, defeating Nao Hibino and Danka Kovinić in the final, 7–5, 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Zhuhai Open - Doubles 2018 Women's Doubles
